      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "水名。即千河，今甘肃、陕西间的河流。",
      "examples": [
        "汧水，出右扶風汧縣西北，入渭。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "汧"
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "水泉出而汇聚为沼泽，或河水溢为沼泽。",
      "examples": [
        "汧，出不流。",
        "水决之泽为汧。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "汧"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "古县名。在今陕西省千阳县，古称“汧阳”。",
      "examples": [
        "汧阳，县名，在陕西省。今作千阳。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "汧"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "古山名。即岍山，在今陕西省陇县西南。",
      "examples": [
        "汧及岐至于荆山，踰于河。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "汧"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "漂，冲击。",
      "examples": [
        "淋或为汧。‘汧，漂也。’"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "汧"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "part_of_speech": "adjective",
      "meaning": "净，清洁。",
      "examples": [],
